\q2 í̠na i̱ gubalini ho haabo haga kegoniore laro.   
\c 60  
\s1 Ngode Datagaliwabehanda pele milo bi lenego ogo  
\q1
\v 1 Ngode Datagaliwabe-o í̠na ina bo taliatagi halu\x + \xo 60.1 \xt 2 Sml 8.13, 1 Bit 18.12\x*  
\q2 inanaga waitigime bo podahana helo  
\q2 yu wahai harigoni ndobe.  
